                            <comment id="12995174" author="thecarlhall" created="Wed, 16 Feb 2011 05:31:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch of suggested solution. The patch changes the assumption from &quot;everything before the last 4 chars are the pid&quot; to &quot;find the last . and assume everything before that is the pid.&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
All files processed will have an extension (.cfg, .config) as checked by the method that calls parsePid, ConfigInstall.setConfig.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
